{"tid":1301140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致：所有抗爭中連登仔麻煩入一入嚟。","createTime":"2019-07-09T14:28:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T15:02:44.000Z","uid":14153,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"317cb4b39c6526a3e2bec44cbf5178cbd6359ca7","tid":1301140,"uid":14153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:28:38.000Z","msg":"本身係CD-Rom,但係睇到連登仔太弱智忍唔住借朋友ac開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我見到連登仔所謂嘅升級就係不斷加訴求落去由五大訴求變成七大訴求，港共政府連你地果五大訴求都睬你地有尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同你地講就算你地加幾多訴求落去個政府都唔會回應你，因為你地所謂嘅抗爭根本威脅唔到港共政府<br />\n你地幾時明白你地嘅訴求就等於向獨裁政府放棄佢嘅獨裁權利比自由你一樣可笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />根本冇可能<br />\n<br />\n但係連登依家充斥着一種階段性勝利開埋啲膠post（etc 寶礦力，周柏豪，連儂牆...咁樣同一四年打飛機自high有咩分別?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktyRcpF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktyRcpF.png&h=2d3b765c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後我想講嘅係香港人需要的是一場革命，而唔係和平遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5f86069ad298cec81650252224c86d49390495","tid":1301140,"uid":89627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:33:34.000Z","msg":"成個熱門都係寶礦力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同尋晚有咩分別？<br />\n尋晚fake自己友，今晩就打飛機！"},{"pid":"88ed4aad47ebc1f1ad25cb7e61a555d80d2feceb","tid":1301140,"uid":69525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:34:56.000Z","msg":"推post推左好撚耐<br />\n由8點幾推到依家<br />\n推極都係寶礦力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c0bae4e1e64e84eb51a2a16acfb9e784144cc94","tid":1301140,"uid":89627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:35:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"08fead7797fc0dfdc3ce2bf5936284a5f700b38a","tid":1301140,"uid":14153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa